{"tid":1789804,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"德國twitter戰線文宣","createTime":"2019-12-19T14:04:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-20T17:58:10.000Z","uid":254330,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c485fde19c65ef59b1b0093ba85141e4e56e630d","tid":1789804,"uid":254330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T14:04:58.000Z","msg":"呢個係德文版嘅關於今日星火被收皮tweet嘅初稿 <br />\n請幫手出tweet plz<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDie Hongkong Polizei hat vier Personen festgenommen und 70 Millionen HKD eingefroren. Die Geld angeh&ouml;rt #SparkAlliance, eine Schl&uuml;sselgruppe um die Hongkong Demonstranten zu unterst&uuml;tzen. Die Polizei sagt, es gebe Anzeichen f&uuml;r Geldw&auml;sche von einer Shell-Firma.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O36iRQy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO36iRQy.jpg&h=437ac49c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n請推到德國<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外自行因應word limit 加上hastag"},{"pid":"4eeef3e8e628e64503eb0121024cdfba2b13dae8","tid":1789804,"uid":88940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T14:05:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://t.me/xmasevehk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fxmasevehk&d=d86Hk5Pgd4X%2FjIl3nTqvfGWzMblEAwKPRhfqpO9yGDY%3D&h=01323201\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/xmasevehk</a><br />\n唔好意思借位<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">經濟攬炒！香港人果七千萬比人搞啊！佢老母仲OT成九億<br />\n1221<br />\n1224<br />\n1225<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><br />\n1224！［行動宜家唔推幾時推？］平安夜 賀佢老母呀！</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1789301\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1789301</a>"},{"pid":"efb1588ee1e02736b5f56445ee9944e112f749f5","tid":1789804,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T14:05:33.000Z","msg":"Twitter組不斷搵緊關於星火tweets入<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">task1</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家除左<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">rt + like + reply</span></span> 之外<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=d86Hk5Pgd4X%2FjIl3nTqvfGWzMblEAwKPRhfqpO9yGDY%3D&h=da6738c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n<br />\n可以去task1入面美國參議員講香港的tweets Reply講星火被凍結資產的事件<br />\n<br />\n記住twitter一定要用reply ，令外國議員見到香港最新狀況/外國媒體報導，先係衝到出國際，如果只係香港人出tweet，大家香港人不斷rt, 都剩係停留響同溫層本地圍爐<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTwitter戰線:要令星火事件上到國際！！！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1789690\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1789690</a>"},{"pid":"77d3e87e9ac18a1361d520c06e8a6fd6d8926d7f","tid":1789804,"uid":254330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T14:05:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3ceed7206170172599abfcbc0269ad78b94a853a","tid":1789804,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T14:06:27.000Z","msg":"推!!!! 有冇邊個德國名人可以@"},{"pid":"762d2129b86f3163f8152995322adc873b721458","tid":1789804,"uid":191271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T14:07:21.000Z","msg":"呢條先係主線呀！<br />\n<br />\n【致英國及美國政府的公開信】 《中英聯合聲明》- 條約簽署之第35年<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1789766\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1789766</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cec14fdddaa828be89f8f46a4e81a2735fdc16cf","tid":1789804,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T14:07:51.000Z","msg":"Twitter戰線:要令星火事件上到國際！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1789690\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1789690</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span 